The '''Anyang Korea Ginseng Corporation''', or '''Anyang KGC''',  is a professional [[basketball]] club in the [[Korean Basketball League]]. They are based at [[Anyang Sports Complex|Anyang Arena]] in the city of [[Anyang, Gyeonggi|Anyang]]. Anyang KGC have won two KBL championship titles, in the  [[2011–12 KBL season|2011–12]] and [[2016–17 KBL season|2016–17]] seasons.

==Team names==
* 1992–1997: '''SBS Basketball Team'''
* 1997–2005: '''Anyang SBS Stars'''
* 2005–2010: '''Anyang KT&G Kites'''
* 2010–2011: '''Anyang Korea Ginseng Corporation'''
* 2011–present: '''Anyang KGC'''

