'''Texmar United''' is a [[Belize]]an [[Association football|football]] team which currently competes in the [[Super League of Belize]], Semipro Division.

Formerly known as Tex Mar Boys, the team is based in [[Mango Creek]].  Their home stadium is [[Michael Ashcroft Stadium]].

